# Delivery Gates

- Before considering a task complete, run the repository gates listed in `AGENTS.md`.
- High-risk changes need explicit human review, especially for `supabase/`, routing, permissions, money flows, and destructive operations.
- If verification cannot be run, say so clearly and treat the result as incomplete.
- Do not describe work as finished when only the UI or documentation changed but the core behavior did not.
